### Get all progress for user
GET http://localhost:3000/api/progress?user_id=aaaaaaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaaaaaaaaaa


### Get progress for specific lesson
GET http://localhost:3000/api/progress/bbbbbbbb-bbbb-bbbb-bbbb-bbbbbbbbbbbb?user_id=aaaaaaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaaaaaaaaaa


### Try lesson progress with invalid lesson id (should return 404)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/progress/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000?user_id=aaaaaaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaaaaaaaaaa


### Update progress (start lesson or update position/time)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/progress/update
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "aaaaaaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaaaaaaaaaa",
  "lesson_id": "bbbbbbbb-bbbb-bbbb-bbbb-bbbbbbbbbbbb",
  "last_position_sec": 120,
  "time_spent_sec": 30,
  "video_completed": false,
  "instructions_completed": false
}


### Update progress again (simulate more watch time)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/progress/update
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "aaaaaaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaaaaaaaaaa",
  "lesson_id": "bbbbbbbb-bbbb-bbbb-bbbb-bbbbbbbbbbbb",
  "last_position_sec": 300,
  "time_spent_sec": 45,
  "video_completed": true,
  "instructions_completed": false
}


### Update instructions completion
POST http://localhost:3000/api/progress/update
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "aaaaaaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaaaaaaaaaa",
  "lesson_id": "bbbbbbbb-bbbb-bbbb-bbbb-bbbbbbbbbbbb",
  "time_spent_sec": 20,
  "video_completed": true,
  "instructions_completed": true
}


### Complete lesson (creates report)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/progress/complete
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "aaaaaaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaaaaaaaaaa",
  "lesson_id": "bbbbbbbb-bbbb-bbbb-bbbb-bbbbbbbbbbbb",
  "self_rating": 4
}


### Try completing lesson without required progress (should fail)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/progress/complete
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "aaaaaaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaaaaaaaaaa",
  "lesson_id": "cccccccc-cccc-cccc-cccc-cccccccccccc"
}


### Get progress summary (for My Progress page)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/progress/summary?user_id=aaaaaaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaaaaaaaaaa